{"tid":1359532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花]社會福利署出現連儂牆！","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T19:49:39.000Z","uid":67073,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0b401f23dc42a5c74d98e2d5c7b85010b96b769f","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"啱啱朋友fw左呢篇文想支持遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們是一班社會福利署的職員。<br />\n<br />\n我們對7月21日晚元朗發生的白衫人襲擊香港市民一事感到痛心。白衫人當晚的野蠻行為不但傷害了在場的市民，亦衝擊了香港的文明社會及損害了香港的核心價值。警方當晚的處理亦令香港人對警隊，甚至對政府服務失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n香港的公務員一直抱著「堅守法治」、「行事客觀、不偏不倚」及「盡忠職守，專業勤奮」的信念服務香港市民。我們現懇請香港警察盡忠職守，嚴正處理元朗白衫人襲擊市民事件，不辱公僕使命。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請政府虛心聆聽社會各界意見，修補社會撕裂。我們寄語各位公務員堅守崗位，繼續為香港市民服務，捍衛公僕尊嚴。我們同時亦呼籲香港市民互相勉勵，向有情緒問題的朋友提供協助。我們絕不希望再看見有任何香港人輕生。<br />\n<br />\n我們會繼續堅守崗位，克盡己任，以專業態度為市民服務。<br />\n<br />\n一班社會福利署職員上<br />\n<br />\n#溫情暖社署<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNhD5vs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNhD5vs.png&h=ce5e3b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">27/7 元朗見</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"96a41c441e1a0b8c3bffc605c8c76180da258ed7","tid":1359532,"uid":274055,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">~證件連儂牆~</span>"},{"pid":"755b94cdd2a62219dbd3a343484755e4089ad0af","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好比何妖轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n光復元朗母忘義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0580382d7e50c4658c2816a6c502363549fb83fa","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b3c56439927eb0168137a08484aa71ad0ab97d","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66ecd53a19c1e19e7b161b6ac115541a02540ae","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3176245687f5e842259394875d10e0d6bbe83002","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2977cd50c6d8700d8b4b1bb52ee6980be6ec22","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53945a9156698f15ed1116dbb2c83f578f1b0f7b","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5975352153c4ddd39f9d34a454b8e3a83295ac08","tid":1359532,"uid":67073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb6cf20e518864826293fcc2608cdbd7772fc72","tid":1359532,"uid":121034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0